'''Jae Lee''' is a [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] artist who provided artwork for a trading card depicting a [[Rancor/Legends|Rancor]] in the ''[[1994 Topps Star Wars Galaxy Series 2]]'' set from [[The Topps Company, Inc.|Topps]].<ref name="Card 243" /> He also provided the cover illustration for [[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine 3|''Star Wars Galaxy'' 3]].<ref name="SWGM 3">[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine 3|''Star Wars Galaxy'' 3]]</ref>

